page.title: Contest Hoodie Order Form
page.content:
Please complete order form below and return with your check made payable to “NRHS Band Boosters” or cash in an envelope labeled “Contest Hoodie” and place it in the white metal box in the band room by August 29, 2016. We would like to have orders filled prior to our first contest.

NO ORDERS WILL BE TAKEN AFTER AUGUST 29.

Checks made payable to: NRHS Band Boosters

Please call Shirley Berish with any questions (440) 717-1532.
